{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58bcd77066","title":"给续范亭的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e65cbe2f85","index":0,"year":1946,"month":1,"day":22,"articleId":"58bcd77066"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"76d13ef57b","type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"58bcd77066"},{"id":"d02676fa20","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年1月22日）范亭同志你打过“潘尼西林”没有？此药虽不治结核菌，但治球菌、螺旋菌有大效，体内此后两类菌如能去掉，则结核延立，有早意之可能。此祝健康","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"58bcd77066"},{"id":"f36c294d75","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"58bcd77066"},{"id":"95144e487a","type":"paragraph","text":"一月二十二日我休养已满两月，有进步，并告[1续范亭（1893-1947），山西省等县（今原平市）西社村人，著名爱国符领。早年参加孙中山领导的同盟会。后在国民党任职，普经隐退一段时间，后与共产党人合作创建山西新军。1947年病道后技迹认为中国共产党正式党员。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"58bcd77066"}],"page":{"id":"84088a0f85","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"58bcd77066","start":155,"end":155}}}},"__N_SSG":true}